(18, '1', 'Post Graduate Diploma (PGD) in Tourism and Hospitality Management', '', '&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;data:image/webp;base64,&quot; width=&quot;900&quot; height=&quot;600&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;The Post Graduate Diploma (PGD) in Tourism &amp;amp; Hospitality Management, certified by Global Center of Excellence, is a comprehensive program designed to equip students with the skills and knowledge required to excel in the dynamic and growing field of tourism and hospitality. Here are some key points about the program:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;1. Program Focus:&lt;/strong&gt; The PGD program is specifically tailored to provide a deep understanding of both the tourism and hospitality sectors. It covers various aspects of management, operations, customer service, and industry trends.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;2. Duration: &lt;/strong&gt;The program typically spans [X] months/semesters, allowing students to quickly acquire specialized knowledge and skills for immediate application in the industry.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;3. Curriculum:&lt;/strong&gt; The curriculum integrates theoretical learning with practical applications. It covers subjects such as hospitality management, tourism marketing, event planning, revenue management, customer experience, and sustainable tourism practices.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;4. Industry-Relevant Skills:&lt;/strong&gt; Students gain hands-on experience and practical skills through workshops, case studies, and industry internships. This prepares them to handle real-world challenges and excel in various roles within the tourism and hospitality sectors.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;5. Faculty: &lt;/strong&gt;The program is taught by experienced professionals and experts in the field, ensuring that students receive up-to-date insights and knowledge aligned with industry best practices.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;6. Guest Lectures and Industry Interaction:&lt;/strong&gt; Regular guest lectures by industry leaders and experts provide students with valuable insights into current trends, challenges, and opportunities in the tourism and hospitality sectors.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;7. Career Opportunities:&lt;/strong&gt; Graduates of the program are well-equipped to pursue a range of career paths, including hotel management, travel and tour operations, event planning, resort management, and more.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;8. Networking:&lt;/strong&gt; The program provides ample opportunities for students to network with industry professionals, alumni, and fellow students, expanding their professional connections within the field.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;9. Practical Projects:&lt;/strong&gt; Students often engage in real-world projects, such as designing marketing campaigns or organizing events, allowing them to apply their theoretical knowledge to practical scenarios.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;10. Global Perspective:&lt;/strong&gt; Many programs offer insights into the global nature of the industry, covering international tourism trends, cross-cultural communication, and the impact of globalization on the field.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;11. Certification and Recognition: &lt;/strong&gt;Successful completion of the PGD program leads to a recognized diploma that can enhance graduates&#039; credibility and employability in the competitive job market.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;12. Optional Specializations:&lt;/strong&gt; Some institutes might offer specialization tracks within the program, allowing students to focus on areas such as hotel management, event management, culinary arts, or sustainable tourism.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;In summary, the Post Graduate Diploma in Tourism &amp;amp; Hospitality Management is a comprehensive program that combines theoretical knowledge with practical skills, preparing graduates for successful careers in the dynamic and diverse tourism and hospitality industry.&lt;/p&gt;', '', 'h2_services_img07.jpg', '', '', '');
INSERT INTO `aa_our_services` (`service_id`, `catg_id`, `title`, `Icon`, `full_text`, `doc_pdf_url`, `image`, `featured_image`, `fee_price`, `facilitator_id`) VALUES
(19, '1', 'Post Graduate Diploma (PGD) in Cyber Security', '', '&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;data:image/jpeg;base64,&quot; width=&quot;900&quot; height=&quot;600&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Duration: 1 year | Mode: Full-time | Accreditation: [Global Center for Excellence LLC]&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Prepare for a dynamic career in the rapidly evolving field of cybersecurity with our comprehensive Post Graduate Diploma program. Designed by industry experts and leading professionals, this program equips you with the knowledge and skills needed to safeguard digital assets, detect and mitigate cyber threats, and ensure the integrity of sensitive information. Through a blend of theoretical learning and hands-on practical experience, you will gain expertise in:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Network Security: &lt;/strong&gt;Understand and implement measures to secure computer networks from unauthorized access, attacks, and breaches.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Cyber Threat Intelligence:&lt;/strong&gt; Learn to analyze and anticipate potential cyber threats, staying one step ahead of cybercriminals.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Incident Response:&lt;/strong&gt; Develop strategies to effectively respond to and manage cyber incidents, minimizing damage and downtime.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Ethical Hacking:&lt;/strong&gt; Master the techniques used by ethical hackers to identify vulnerabilities and strengthen system defenses.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Data Protection:&lt;/strong&gt; Explore encryption methods, access controls, and privacy regulations to ensure the confidentiality of sensitive data.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Security Auditing:&lt;/strong&gt; Learn to conduct thorough security audits to assess and enhance an organization&#039;s cybersecurity posture.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;By the end of the program, you&#039;ll be equipped with the skills to contribute significantly to organizations&#039; cybersecurity efforts, protecting them from ever-evolving digital threats. Join us at the Global Center for Excellence and embark on a journey towards a rewarding and impactful career in the realm of cybersecurity.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', '', 'h2_services_img01.jpg', '', '', '');
INSERT INTO `aa_our_services` (`service_id`, `catg_id`, `title`, `Icon`, `full_text`, `doc_pdf_url`, `image`, `featured_image`, `fee_price`, `facilitator_id`) VALUES
(20, '1', 'Post Graduate Diploma (PGD) in Learning and Development', '', '&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;data:image/webp;base64,&quot; width=&quot;902&quot; height=&quot;601&quot;&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;The Post Graduate Diploma (PGD) in Learning &amp;amp; Development certified by Global Center for Excellence is a comprehensive and specialized program designed to equip students with the skills and knowledge necessary to excel in the field of learning and development. This program is tailored for individuals aspiring to build a career in corporate training, education, human resources, or organizational development.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Throughout the program, students will engage with a wide range of topics, including adult learning theories, instructional design principles, performance management, talent development, and employee engagement strategies. The curriculum integrates both theoretical concepts and practical applications, enabling students to develop a deep understanding of how to create effective learning experiences and enhance organizational performance.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Key highlights of the PGD in Learning &amp;amp; Development program:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Holistic Curriculum: The curriculum is carefully crafted to cover various aspects of learning and development, including curriculum design, training methodologies, e-learning technologies, assessment techniques, and more.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Expert Faculty: Students will learn from experienced professionals and industry experts who bring real-world insights and best practices to the classroom.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Practical Experience: The program emphasizes hands-on learning through projects, case studies, and practical exercises, allowing students to apply their knowledge in simulated or real-world settings.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Industry-Relevant Skills: Graduates will be equipped with the skills needed to design, implement, and evaluate training programs that align with organizational goals and enhance employee capabilities.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Networking Opportunities: Students will have the chance to interact with peers, faculty, and industry professionals, fostering valuable connections that can be beneficial for future career opportunities.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Career Prospects: The PGD in Learning &amp;amp; Development opens doors to a range of career paths, including corporate training, instructional design, e-learning development, HR roles, and organizational development positions.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Flexible Learning Options: The program is offered in various formats, including part-time and online options, catering to the needs of working professionals and individuals with different schedules.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;By completing the Post Graduate Diploma in Learning &amp;amp; Development, students will be well-prepared to contribute to the growth and success of organizations by designing and implementing effective learning solutions that drive employee performance and development.&lt;/p&gt;', '', 'h2_services_img04.jpg', '', '', '');
INSERT INTO `aa_our_services` (`service_id`, `catg_id`, `title`, `Icon`, `full_text`, `doc_pdf_url`, `image`, `featured_image`, `fee_price`, `facilitator_id`) VALUES
(21, '1', 'Post Graduate Diploma (PGD) in Digital Marketing', '', '&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;data:image/jpeg;base64,&quot; width=&quot;901&quot; height=&quot;507&quot;&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Program Overview:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;The PGD in Digital Marketing is a comprehensive program designed to equip students with the skills and knowledge needed to excel in the rapidly evolving field of digital marketing.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Duration:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;The program typically spans over a period of 12 months, divided into multiple semesters or modules.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Curriculum:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;text-align: justify;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun: yes;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;The curriculum covers a wide range of topics within digital marketing, including but not limited to:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;ul&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun: yes;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;Fundamentals of Digital Marketing&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun: yes;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;Search Engine Optimization (SEO)&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun: yes;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun: yes;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;Social Media Marketing&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun: yes;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;Pay-Per-Click (PPC) Advertising&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun: yes;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;Email Marketing&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun: yes;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;Content Marketing&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun: yes;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;Analytics and Data Interpretation&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun: yes;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;E-commerce Strategies&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun: yes;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp; &lt;/span&gt;Mobile Marketing&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Hands-on Experience:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun: yes;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;The program emphasizes hands-on learning, providing students with real-world projects and simulations to apply theoretical knowledge to practical scenarios.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Industry Experts:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Students will learn from experienced digital marketing professionals and industry experts, gaining insights into the latest trends and best practices.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Case Studies:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;The curriculum includes analysis of real-life case studies, enabling students to understand how digital marketing strategies are implemented by various businesses.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Certifications:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Upon successful completion of the program, students will receive certificates from Global Center of Excellence, which can add value to their resumes and validate their expertise.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Networking Opportunities:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;The program offers opportunities to connect with peers, alumni, and industry professionals through workshops, seminars, and networking events.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Career Prospects:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Graduates of the PGD in Digital Marketing are well-equipped to pursue careers in various roles such as Digital Marketing Manager, Social Media Specialist, SEO Analyst, Content Strategist, and more.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Flexible Learning:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;The program may offer flexible learning options, including part-time or online formats, making it accessible to working professionals and those with busy schedules.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Admission Requirements:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Prospective students might need a bachelor&#039;s degree in any discipline from a recognized university. Some programs may also consider relevant work experience.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Future-Ready Skills:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Graduates will have a strong understanding of digital marketing trends, analytics, and tools, positioning them as valuable assets in the digital era.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Continuous Learning:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;The dynamic nature of digital marketing requires professionals to stay updated. The PGD serves as a foundation for lifelong learning and adaptation to industry changes.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;This Post Graduate Diploma in Digital Marketing equips students with a solid foundation in the world of digital marketing, preparing them for success in an increasingly digital-driven business landscape.&lt;/p&gt;', '', 'h2_services_img01.jpg', '', '', '');
INSERT INTO `aa_our_services` (`service_id`, `catg_id`, `title`, `Icon`, `full_text`, `doc_pdf_url`, `image`, `featured_image`, `fee_price`, `facilitator_id`) VALUES
(22, '1', 'Post Graduate Diploma (PGD) in Intellectual Property Rights', '', '&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 11.0pt; line-height: 107%; font-family: &#039;Calibri&#039;,sans-serif; mso-ascii-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-fareast-font-family: Calibri; mso-fareast-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-hansi-theme-font: minor-latin; mso-bidi-font-family: &#039;Times New Roman&#039;; mso-bidi-theme-font: minor-bidi; mso-ansi-language: EN-US; mso-fareast-language: EN-US; mso-bidi-language: AR-SA;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;data:image/jpeg;base64,&quot; width=&quot;903&quot; height=&quot;849&quot;&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&quot;Enhance your expertise in the dynamic realm of Intellectual Property Rights (IPR) with our comprehensive Post Graduate Diploma program. Designed by the Global Center for Excellence, this specialized course empowers participants with a deep understanding of the legal, ethical, and commercial dimensions of intellectual property. Through a blend of rigorous coursework and real-world case studies, you&#039;ll gain proficiency in patent, trademark, copyright, and trade secret laws, while also exploring the intricacies of technology transfer and IP valuation. Equip yourself with the knowledge to navigate the complexities of protecting and managing intellectual property in today&#039;s innovation-driven world. Join us to embark on a journey that merges legal acumen with business acumen, fostering a new generation of IPR leaders.&quot;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;h4 class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Key Points:&lt;/h4&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Comprehensive Curriculum&lt;/strong&gt;: Our program covers a wide spectrum of intellectual property topics, including patents, trademarks, copyrights, and trade secrets, providing a holistic understanding of IPR.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Expert Faculty:&lt;/strong&gt; Learn from seasoned professionals and legal experts who bring real-world insights and experiences into the classroom.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Case-Based Learning:&lt;/strong&gt; Analyze real case studies to grasp the practical application of IPR principles in various industries and scenarios.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Technology Transfer:&lt;/strong&gt; Explore the strategies and legal frameworks involved in transferring technology and leveraging intellectual property for business growth.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;IP Valuation:&lt;/strong&gt; Understand the methodologies and processes to assess the value of intellectual property assets, a crucial skill in negotiations and business transactions.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Legal and Ethical Dimensions:&lt;/strong&gt; Delve into the ethical considerations and legal intricacies of intellectual property protection, enforcement, and global perspectives.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Industry-Relevant Insights:&lt;/strong&gt; Gain insights into the evolving landscape of IPR in the context of emerging technologies, digital media, and international trade.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Networking Opportunities:&lt;/strong&gt; Connect with fellow participants, industry experts, and potential employers, fostering valuable professional relationships.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Flexible Learning:&lt;/strong&gt; Our program offers both in-person and online learning options, accommodating diverse learning preferences and schedules.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Career Advancement:&lt;/strong&gt; Equip yourself with a specialized skill set that opens doors to roles such as IP analyst, patent examiner, legal consultant, and more, in industries ranging from technology to entertainment.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;Elevate your knowledge in Intellectual Property Rights through our PGD program and become a proficient practitioner equipped to tackle the challenges of the modern intellectual property landscape.&quot;&lt;/p&gt;', '', 'h2_services_img05.jpg', '', '', '');
INSERT INTO `aa_our_services` (`service_id`, `catg_id`, `title`, `Icon`, `full_text`, `doc_pdf_url`, `image`, `featured_image`, `fee_price`, `facilitator_id`) VALUES
(23, '2', 'Certified Soft Skills Trainer', '', '&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt; text-align: center;&quot; align=&quot;center&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 16.0pt; line-height: 107%;&quot;&gt;Certified Soft Skills Trainer&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun: yes;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Course Overview:&lt;/strong&gt; The Certified Soft Skills Trainer program is designed to equip participants with the skills and knowledge needed to become proficient trainers in teaching essential soft skills. Through a comprehensive curriculum, participants will learn effective training methodologies, facilitation techniques, and assessment strategies to help individuals develop critical interpersonal and communication skills.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Course Duration:&lt;/strong&gt; 10 weeks (duration can be customized based on program needs)&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Course Objectives:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;ul style=&quot;margin-top: 0in;&quot; type=&quot;disc&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list .5in;&quot;&gt;Understand the significance of soft skills in personal and professional success.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list .5in;&quot;&gt;Acquire practical skills to design and deliver engaging soft skills training programs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list .5in;&quot;&gt;Develop effective facilitation techniques for interactive learning experiences.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list .5in;&quot;&gt;Learn methods to assess and measure participants&#039; soft skills development.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list .5in;&quot;&gt;Create a diverse toolkit of training materials for various soft skill topics.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Course Modules:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;ol style=&quot;margin-top: 0in;&quot; start=&quot;1&quot; type=&quot;1&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l4 level1 lfo2; tab-stops: list .5in;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Introduction to Soft Skills Training:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;ul style=&quot;margin-top: 0in;&quot; type=&quot;disc&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l4 level2 lfo2; tab-stops: list 1.0in;&quot;&gt;Exploring the importance of soft skills in the modern workplace.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l4 level2 lfo2; tab-stops: list 1.0in;&quot;&gt;Identifying key soft skills for different roles and industries.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l4 level2 lfo2; tab-stops: list 1.0in;&quot;&gt;Understanding the impact of soft skills on communication, teamwork, and leadership.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0in 0in .0001pt 1.0in;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;ol style=&quot;margin-top: 0in;&quot; start=&quot;2&quot; type=&quot;1&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l4 level1 lfo2; tab-stops: list .5in;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Designing Effective Soft Skills Training Programs:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;ul style=&quot;margin-top: 0in;&quot; type=&quot;disc&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l4 level2 lfo2; tab-stops: list 1.0in;&quot;&gt;Analyzing training needs and defining learning objectives.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l4 level2 lfo2; tab-stops: list 1.0in;&quot;&gt;Structuring comprehensive soft skills training curricula.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l4 level2 lfo2; tab-stops: list 1.0in;&quot;&gt;Incorporating engaging activities, case studies, and role plays.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0in 0in .0001pt 1.0in;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;ol style=&quot;margin-top: 0in;&quot; start=&quot;3&quot; type=&quot;1&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l4 level1 lfo2; tab-stops: list .5in;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Interactive Facilitation Techniques:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;ul style=&quot;margin-top: 0in;&quot; type=&quot;disc&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l4 level2 lfo2; tab-stops: list 1.0in;&quot;&gt;Techniques for cr