personal Skills:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;ul style=&quot;margin-top: 0in;&quot; type=&quot;disc&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l4 level2 lfo2; tab-stops: list 1.0in;&quot;&gt;Developing clear and effective communication skills.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l4 level2 lfo2; tab-stops: list 1.0in;&quot;&gt;Enhancing active listening and empathy.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l4 level2 lfo2; tab-stops: list 1.0in;&quot;&gt;Adapting communication style to diverse audiences.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0in 0in .0001pt 1.0in;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;ol style=&quot;margin-top: 0in;&quot; start=&quot;6&quot; type=&quot;1&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l4 level1 lfo2; tab-stops: list .5in;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Teamwork, Collaboration, and Conflict Resolution:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;ul style=&quot;margin-top: 0in;&quot; type=&quot;disc&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l4 level2 lfo2; tab-stops: list 1.0in;&quot;&gt;Fostering effective teamwork and collaboration.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l4 level2 lfo2; tab-stops: list 1.0in;&quot;&gt;Strategies for managing conflicts and promoting positive interactions.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l4 level2 lfo2; tab-stops: list 1.0in;&quot;&gt;Building strong working relationships within teams.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0in 0in .0001pt 1.0in;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;ol style=&quot;margin-top: 0in;&quot; start=&q