3; tab-stops: list .5in;&quot;&gt;Successful completion leads to a &quot;Certified Soft Skills Trainer&quot; certificate.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who Should Attend:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;ul style=&quot;margin-top: 0in;&quot; type=&quot;disc&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo4; tab-stops: list .5in;&quot;&gt;Aspiring trainers looking to specialize in soft skills development.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo4; tab-stops: list .5in;&quot;&gt;Experienced trainers aiming to enhance their facilitation techniques.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo4; tab-stops: list .5in;&quot;&gt;HR professionals and educators involved in soft skills training.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Course Benefits:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;ul style=&quot;margin-top: 0in;&quot; type=&quot;disc&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo5; tab-stops: list .5in;&quot;&gt;Comprehensive understanding of essential soft skills and their applications.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo5; tab-stops: list .5in;&quot;&gt;Proficiency in designing engaging and effective soft skills training programs.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo5; tab-stops: list .5in;&quot;&gt