(24, '2', 'Certified Emotional Intelligence (EI) Professional', '', '&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;data:image/png;base64,&quot; width=&quot;902&quot; height=&quot;506&quot;&gt;&lt;br&gt;Course Overview:&lt;/strong&gt; The Certified Emotional Intelligence (EI) Professional program is designed to provide participants with a deep understanding of emotional intelligence and its significance in personal and professional success. Through a comprehensive curriculum that combines theoretical knowledge with practical applications, participants will develop the skills needed to enhance emotional intelligence and positively impact interactions, relationships, and leadership capabilities.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Course Duration:&lt;/strong&gt; 10 weeks&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Course Objectives:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;ul style=&quot;margin-top: 0in;&quot; type=&quot;disc&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list .5in;&quot;&gt;Understand the core concepts and components of emotional intelligence.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list .5in;&quot;&gt;Develop self-awareness and self-regulation for emotional well-being.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list .5in;&quot;&gt;Cultivate empathy and improve interpersonal relationships.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list .5in;&quot;&gt;Enhance communication skills and conflict resolution abilities.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list .5in;&quot;&gt;Apply emotional intelligence principles to leadership and decision-making.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l2 level1 lfo1; tab-stops: list .5in;&quot;&gt;Develop strategies for fostering emotional intelligence in others.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Course Modules:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;ol style=&quot;margin-top: 0in;&quot; start=&quot;1&quot; type=&quot;1&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2; tab-stops: list .5in;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Introduction to Emotional Intelligence (EI):&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;ul style=&quot;margin-top: 0in;&quot; type=&quot;disc&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l0 level2 lfo2; tab-stops: list 1.0in;&quot;&gt;Understanding emotional intelligence and its significance.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l0 level2 lfo2; tab-stops: list 1.0in;&quot;&gt;Components of EI: Self-awareness, self-regulation, empathy, motivation, and social skills.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l0 level2 lfo2; tab-stops: list 1.0in;&quot;&gt;Benefits of high emotional intelligence in personal and professional contexts.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0in 0in .0001pt 1.0in;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;ol style=&quot;margin-top: 0in;&quot; start=&quot;2&quot; type=&quot;1&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2; tab-stops: list .5in;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Self-awareness and Self-regulation:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;ul style=&quot;margin-top: 0in;&quot; type=&quot;disc&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l0 level2 lfo2; tab-stops: list 1.0in;&quot;&gt;Assessing and understanding one&#039;s emotions and triggers.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l0 level2 lfo2; tab-stops: list 1.0in;&quot;&gt;Techniques for managing and regulating emotions effectively.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l0 level2 lfo2; tab-stops: list 1.0in;&quot;&gt;Building resilience and emotional balance.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0in 0in .0001pt 1.0in;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;ol style=&quot;margin-top: 0in;&quot; start=&quot;3&quot; type=&quot;1&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2; tab-stops: list .5in;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Empathy and Interpersonal Relationships:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;ul style=&quot;margin-top: 0in;&quot; type=&quot;disc&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l0 level2 lfo2; tab-stops: list 1.0in;&quot;&gt;Developing empathy and understanding others&#039; emotions.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l0 level2 lfo2; tab-stops: list 1.0in;&quot;&gt;Effective communication and active listening skills.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l0 level2 lfo2; tab-stops: list 1.0in;&quot;&gt;Building and maintaining positive interpersonal relationships.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0in 0in .0001pt 1.0in;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;ol style=&quot;margin-top: 0in;&quot; start=&quot;4&quot; type=&quot;1&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2; tab-stops: list .5in;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Communication and Conflict Resolution:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;ul style=&quot;margin-top: 0in;&quot; type=&quot;disc&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l0 level2 lfo2; tab-stops: list 1.0in;&quot;&gt;Using emotional intelligence to improve communication.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l0 level2 lfo2; tab-stops: list 1.0in;&quot;&gt;Conflict resolution strategies based on EI principles.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l0 level2 lfo2; tab-stops: list 1.0in;&quot;&gt;Navigating difficult conversations with emotional intelligence.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0in 0in .0001pt 1.0in;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;ol style=&quot;margin-top: 0in;&quot; start=&quot;5&quot; type=&quot;1&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2; tab-stops: list .5in;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Emotional Intelligence in Leadership:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;ul style=&quot;margin-top: 0in;&quot; type=&quot;disc&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l0 level2 lfo2; tab-stops: list 1.0in;&quot;&gt;Leading with emotional intelligence and authenticity.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l0 level2 lfo2; tab-stops: list 1.0in;&quot;&gt;EI&#039;s impact on decision-making and problem-solving.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l0 level2 lfo2; tab-stops: list 1.0in;&quot;&gt;Motivating and inspiring teams using emotional intelligence.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l0 level1 lfo2; tab-stops: list .5in;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Fostering Emotional Intelligence in Others:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;ul style=&quot;margin-top: 0in;&quot; type=&quot;disc&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l0 level2 lfo2; tab-stops: list 1.0in;&quot;&gt;Teaching and promoting EI in professional and personal settings.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l0 level2 lfo2; tab-stops: list 1.0in;&quot;&gt;Coaching and mentoring techniques to enhance others&#039; EI.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l0 level2 lfo2; tab-stops: list 1.0in;&quot;&gt;Creating an emotionally intelligent organizational culture.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;/ol&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0in 0in .0001pt 1.0in;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Assessment and Certification:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;ul style=&quot;margin-top: 0in;&quot; type=&quot;disc&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l4 level1 lfo3; tab-stops: list .5in;&quot;&gt;Active participation in discussions, reflections, and exercises.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l4 level1 lfo3; tab-stops: list .5in;&quot;&gt;Completion of assignments and real-world EI projects.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l4 level1 lfo3; tab-stops: list .5in;&quot;&gt;Presentation of a final project applying EI principles in a real-world context.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l4 level1 lfo3; tab-stops: list .5in;&quot;&gt;Successful completion results in a &quot;Certified Emotional Intelligence Professional&quot; certificate.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Who Should Attend:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;ul style=&quot;margin-top: 0in;&quot; type=&quot;disc&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l3 level1 lfo4; tab-stops: list .5in;&quot;&gt;Professionals seeking to develop strong emotional intelligence skills.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l3 level1 lfo4; tab-stops: list .5in;&quot;&gt;Managers and leaders aiming to expand their EI competencies.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l3 level1 lfo4; tab-stops: list .5in;&quot;&gt;Coaches, mentors, and educators interested in promoting EI in others.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin: 0in 0in .0001pt .5in;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Course Benefits:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;ul style=&quot;margin-top: 0in;&quot; type=&quot;disc&quot;&gt;\r\n&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo5; tab-stops: list .5in;&quot;&gt;In-depth understanding of emotional intelligence principles and components.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo5; tab-stops: list .5in;&quot;&gt;Improved self-awareness, self-regulation, and interpersonal skills.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo5; tab-stops: list .5in;&quot;&gt;Enhanced communication and conflict resolution capabilities.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo5; tab-stops: list .5in;&quot;&gt;Leadership abilities enriched by emotional intelligence.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;li class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt; mso-list: l1 level1 lfo5; tab-stops: list .5in;&quot;&gt;Recognition as a Certified Emotional Intelligence Professional.&lt;/li&gt;\r\n&lt;/ul&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: .0001pt;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;', '', 'h2_services_img02.jpg', '', '', '');
INSERT INTO `aa_our_services` (`service_id`, `catg_id`, `title`, `Icon`, `full_text`, `doc_pdf_url`, `image`, `featured_image`, `fee_price`, `facilitator_id`) VALUES
(26, '4', 'IFC (International Finance Corporation) TOT', '', '&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;Join Bangladesh&#039;s one and only IFC (International Finance Corporation) TOT!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;Train like a Pro!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;Facilitating Face-to-Face Learning - Online Version (FFF-O)&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;A Training of Trainers (TOT) Course for Facilitating Learning by IFC&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;Not your ordinary TOT.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;Facilitator&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;QUAZI M. AHMED&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;LLB., MBA (IBA), MA (Japan), IMP (NYU, USA), CISS (Norway)&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;IFC Certified Master Trainer&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: red;&quot;&gt;Founder &amp;amp; CEO, Global Center of Excellence LLC.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;Founder &amp;amp; President, BOLD&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Six Sessions | 12 Hours&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;Following are the dates and times:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;Pre-course Webinar: Tuesday, Sep 12, 2023, 22:00 to 23:30 (GMT+6)&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;Session 1. Friday, Sep 15, 2023, 20:00 to 22:00 (GMT+6)&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;Session 2. Saturday, Sep 16, 2023, 20:00 to 22:00 (GMT+6)&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;Session 3. Saturday, Sep 23, 2023, 20:00 to 22:00 (GMT+6)&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;Session 4. Monday, Sep 25, 2023, 20:00 to 22:00 (GMT+6)&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;Session 5. Friday, Sep 29, 2023, 20:00 to 22:00 (GMT+6)&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;Session 6. Saturday, Oct 7, 2023, 20:00 to 22:00 (GMT+6)&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;Please Note!&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;? Certificate of Completion awarded by IFC, World Bank Group, with &lt;span style=&quot;color: red;&quot;&gt;FutureLeaders&lt;/span&gt;&amp;trade; as its accredited provider.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;? TOT graduates will be invited to enroll in the IFC-LPI Certified Trainer course and will get opportunities to work as volunteer trainers with Quazi M. Ahmed in some of his assignments with clients (conditions apply).&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: black; mso-themecolor: text1;&quot;&gt;? Fee for this Training of Trainers (TOT) is BDT 19,550/- including 15% VAT.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: black; mso-themecolor: text1;&quot;&gt;? Early bird fee is BDT 17,250/-(Including 15% VAT) and one must register by Sep 07, 2023, to get this discount.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;? Last date of registration is Sep 10, 2023.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;Contact Us&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;Floor 1/B, House 4A, Road 84, Gulshan 2, Dhaka 1212&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;+8801843640517 (Tanvir)&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;+8801969377122 (Wakil)&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;facebook/&lt;span style=&quot;color: red;&quot;&gt;futureleaders.bd&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;quazi.ahmed@&lt;span style=&quot;color: red;&quot;&gt;futureleadersgroup.com&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: red;&quot;&gt;www.futureleaders.asia&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;Organized by: &lt;span style=&quot;color: red;&quot;&gt;FutureLeaders&amp;trade;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;Registration form: &lt;span style=&quot;color: red;&quot;&gt;https://forms.gle/pcwk5RUTEi3biKSQ8&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;Based on the feedback of practitioners from diverse sectors across 50+ countries of the world, our TOT course is designed to help you prepare and deliver training that transforms people. Are you ready to level up as a trainer?&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;Why Take This Course?&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;IFC has trained and certified more than 3500 trainers from all over the world, giving you access to an international network of professionals. Taking the TOT course will enable you to deliver powerful learning experiences to adult participants that can help improve their capability, capacity, productivity, and performance. The TOT is based on best practice principles and learning methods such as:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;? Learners enjoy taking responsibility for their own learning. The TOT approach is guided by how adults learn best.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;? People tend to learn better by doing. Interactive approaches are used to optimize learning.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;? Adults learn considerably from each other. Communication among learners in class is encouraged.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;Who Will Benefit from This Course?&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;1) Professional trainers aiming to improve and achieve professional recognition.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;2) Novice trainers looking to upgrade their facilitation skills to a professional level.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;3) Managers with direct responsibility for training programs.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;4) Administrators having quality assurance responsibility for training programs.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;What Will I Learn?&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;The course is designed to equip you with the key competencies of training:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;1 - Master the training cycle&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;? Prepare for training&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;? Introduce training session&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;? Present training content&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;? Give and receive feedback&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;? Conclude a training session&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;? Review the training&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;? Report on success of training&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;2 - Manage sessions professionally&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;? Create comfortable environments&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;? Accommodate different learners&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;? Use projectors and slides effectively&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;? Manage session time&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;? Handle difficult circumstances&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;? Use powerful body language&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;? Diffuse gender bias&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;Who Will Train Me?&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;Quazi M. Ahmed, an IFC Certified Master Trainer, has been chosen from a highly selective pool of professionals as your facilitator.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;What Training Methods Will Be Used?&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;1. Group discussions&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;2. Case studies&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;3. Role plays&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;4. Mini-lectures&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;5. Individual demonstrations&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;How is it offered?&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;This program includes 6 modules, spread over 20 days, for a total of 12 instructional hours. In between the sessions, participants will be expected to complete a total of 18 hours of self-study work and participate in group exercises. Participants will also be required to submit videos of themselves facilitating a 5-minute and a 15-minute training segment using the techniques taught in the course.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;Will I receive a certificate at the end of the course?&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;Yes, participants will receive the certificate of completion of the &quot;Facilitating Learning: Online and In-Person&quot; course provided that they:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;? Complete the prerequisite Foundations of Learning course&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;? Attend at least 80% of the &quot;Facilitating Learning: Online and In-Person&quot; course&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;? Complete all course assignments&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;What More is in it for Me?&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;The TOT is also recognized by the Learning and Performance Institute (LPI), a global leading authority on learning and development. TOT graduates qualify to apply for IFC-LPI&amp;rsquo;s Trainer Performance Monitoring &amp;amp; Assessment (TPMA), an internationally recognized trainer certification.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;For more information on the LPI please visit www.thelpi.org&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;For more information on the IFC-LPI TPMA certification please visit www.thelpi.org/certification/tpma-if&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;About the Facilitator&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;QUAZI M. AHMED&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;LLB., MBA (IBA), MA (Japan), IMP (NYU, USA), CISS (Norway)&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;IFC Certified Master Trainer&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: red;&quot;&gt;Founder &amp;amp; CEO, Global Center of Excellence LLC.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;Founder &amp;amp; President, BOLD&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;Educated and trained in Bangladesh, the US, Norway, and Japan, Quazi M. Ahmed&amp;mdash; is a renowned subject matter expert and thought leader with 27 years of experience in training, teaching, speaking, and coaching. Since January 2022, he has been the only IFC/World Bank Group Certified Master Trainer in Bangladesh. Over the years, he has conducted face-to-face training programs/and given talks in the USA, Denmark, Malaysia, India, Nepal, Afghanistan, and Bangladesh&amp;mdash;his home country. He has also done VILT (Virtual Instructor-Led Training) workshops, spoke at e-Conferences and webinars for audiences in dozen other countries including UK, Myanmar, Singapore, New Zealand and Australia&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;For his global presence in the areas of training, Mr. Ahmed received the &amp;ldquo;Global Training and Development Leadership Award&amp;rdquo; in February 2017 by the World HRD Congress in its 25th-anniversary celebrations. By now, he has facilitated training sessions attended by more than one hundred thousand people in the nonprofit, private, and public sectors in multiple countries.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;In recent years, he has completed the following certifications: IFC/World Bank Group Certified Master Trainer, Certified Facilitator from Inside Out Coaching/Development (USA), Certified L&amp;amp;D Professional from Aon Hewitt Learning Center (UK &amp;amp; India), and Certified PPA Practitioner from Thomas Assessment Pvt. Ltd. (UK &amp;amp; India).&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;Mr. Ahmed is recognized as the pioneer of the modern approach to L&amp;amp;D in Bangladesh-the country of his birth. In 2016, he founded the Bangladesh Organization for Learning and Development (BOLD) which is the apex national body serving the needs of trainers, Learning &amp;amp; Development professionals, and others passionate about personal and professional development. One of Quazi&amp;rsquo;s main purposes in life is to become the best version of himself by practicing humility and confidence in his personal and professional spheres.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;Prerequisites of the Course&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;Prerequisites of this course consist of 4 online learning experiences that participants must complete before starting the instructor-led portion of the class:&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;? Maximizing Learning: This learning experience introduces some key theories and techniques that are the basis for our approach to training and which are discussed in more depth during the Facilitating Face-to-Face Learning in-person learning experience. (Duration: 30 minutes)&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;? The Training Lifecycle: This learning experience introduces the industry-standard methodology for providing high-quality training products and services, and places the Facilitating Face-to-Face Learning in-person learning experience in context. (Duration: 25 minutes)&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;? Ethics for Performance and Learning Consultants: This learning experience helps participants consider the best way to respond to the most common ethical dilemmas they might face as performance and learning professionals. It offers a tool and guidance for how to make decisions that protect and enhance themselves, their business, and the profession as a whole in both the short and long terms.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;(Duration: 20 minutes)&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;? Finding Your Path for Facilitation: This learning experience helps participants learn a little about themselves and their comfort level with facilitating training. They need to complete, print, and bring their completed self-assessment with them to the Facilitating Face-to-Face Learning in-person learning experience.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot; style=&quot;margin-bottom: 0in;&quot;&gt;(Duration:10 minutes)&lt;/p&gt;', '', 'h2_services_img07.jpg', 'services_details03.jpg', '', '');

