(4, 'Md Tanvir Hasan', 'Web Developer', '', '', '', '&lt;p&gt;I am Tanvir Hasan, a skilled freelancer with 8 years of experience in web development, web design, WordPress, PHP development, and SEO.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;color: var(--bs-body-color); font-family: var(--bs-body-font-family); font-size: var(--bs-body-font-size); font-weight: var(--bs-body-font-weight); text-align: var(--bs-body-text-align);&quot;&gt;My expertise in these fields allows me to deliver high-quality solutions that meet the unique requirements of each client. With my knowledge and dedication, I can help you achieve your online goals and improve your digital presence.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;', 'h2_team_img03.jpg'),
(5, 'Quazi M. Ahmed', 'Founder & CEO, Global Center of Excellence, LLC, New York, USA', '+13478561274', 'quazi@quazi.global', 'Level 1, House 4/A, Road 84, Gulshan 2, Dhaka 1212', '&lt;p&gt;&lt;em&gt;IMP (New York University, USA), CISS (Univ. of Olso, Norway)&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;MA (Int&amp;rsquo;l Univ. of Japan), MBA (IBA, Univ. of Dhaka, Bangladesh)&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;IFC-Certified Master Trainer in Facilitating Learning&lt;/em&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;em&gt;Certified Facilitator, Grow Model of Coaching (InsideOut Coaching)&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Founder &amp;amp; CEO of the New York-based consulting firm &lt;strong&gt;Global Center of Excellence, LLC,&lt;/strong&gt; Quazi M. Ahmed is an IFC (of the World Bank Group) Certified Master Trainer. He is a global trainer whose assignments over the years have taken him to many parts of the world including countries such as (alphabetically) Afghanistan, Bangladesh, Canada, Denmark, India, Malaysia, Nepal, Thailand, the UK, and the US.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Since March 2023, he is one of the Facilitators of the &lt;strong&gt;International Leadership Program (ILP) of PUMA Group&lt;/strong&gt;. As part of this role, he has already delivered a workshop in Bangkok in May 2023 and his upcoming assignments are scheduled in Thailand (Sept.&amp;rsquo;23), Vietnam (Dec.&amp;rsquo;23), and Taiwan (March &amp;rsquo;24).&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;When it comes to his formal education, he attended the following universities: Stern School of Business, New York University, USA; University of Oslo, Norway; International University of Japan, Niigata, Japan; and IBA, University of Dhaka, Bangladesh.&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;His clients include but are not limited to:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;MNCs and Joint-ventures:&lt;/strong&gt; Marks &amp;amp; Spencer, Linde Bangladesh, H&amp;amp;M, Coats, Grameenphone, Robi, ACI Godrej Agrovet Pvt. Ltd., &lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun: yes;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;Karnaphuli Fertilizer Company Limited (KAFCO), Standard Chartered Bank, Brac Bank ldt. Nestle &lt;br&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;UN Agencies, INGOs, and Non-profits:&lt;/strong&gt;UNDP, UNHCR, IFPRI, UNOPS, CARE, OXFAM, &lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun: yes;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;Save the chidren &lt;br&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;Governments Agencies:&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;Bangladesh Goverment&lt;/strong&gt;: &lt;span style=&quot;mso-spacerun: yes;&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;Bangladesh Army, LICT, BD Police, Coast Guard, DESCO, WASA, Bangladesh Computer Councill. &lt;br&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;U.S. Government:&lt;/strong&gt; USAID, U.S Embassy in Bangladesh&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;Malaysian Goverment:&lt;/strong&gt; Labuan IBFC&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;Afghanistan Government&lt;/strong&gt;: Ministry of Labor &amp;amp; Social Affairs&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p class=&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;German Government&lt;/strong&gt;: GIZ&lt;br style=&quot;mso-special-character: line-break;&quot;&gt;&lt;!-- [if !supportLineBreakNewLine]--&gt;&lt;br style=&quot;mso-special-character: line-break;&quot;&gt;&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 14pt;&quot;&gt;&lt;strong style=&quot;mso-bidi-font-weight: normal;&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 107%; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;National Group of Companies&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;line-height: 107%; font-family: Calibri, sans-serif;&quot;&gt;: UCB Stock BreakerageLdt. , Square Group, Energypac, BSRM, Seven Ring Cemet, Navana Group, Summit Communications Ltd, AB Bank Ltd., &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;\r\n&lt;p&gt;Speaking of Quazi as a human being, he doesn&amp;rsquo;t shy away from creating a well-rounded and fulfilling approach to life. First, almost every day he reflects on the meaning of life as it gives him a fulfilling and enlightening pursuit. Secondly, his regular meditations bring him inner peace and clarity. Third, traveling with family and alone allows him to create beautiful memories and deepen bonds. Finally, reading books is an excellent way for him to expand his knowledge and gain new perspectives on work and life.&lt;/p&gt;', 'h2_team_img01.jpg');

